reviewText: Ordered 4 Coast Guard titles - all excellent
VINTAGE FILMS OF THE COAST GUARD DURING WW II.  A GOOD OVERVIEW OF THE COAST GUARD ROLE IN WW II.
Being in the Navy, we do have a different mission than the Coast Guard, but protection of the seas and ports is what we do.
Great videos of the CG in action during War Time.  This video has quality imaging and shows great detail.  Not a poor quality product at all.  Would purchase from seller again.
